(21, 1, '2020-09-26 09:53:38', '2020-09-26 01:53:38', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":17,\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-top\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"https://dlcph.com/read/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/founder.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-17 size-full\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"className\":\"jt\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt has-normal-font-size\">First of all, we would like to congratulate you in your desire to improve yourself and your lifestyle through our industry called Multi-Level Marketing (MLM) and we hope this is the vehicle that will help you discover your dreams and your full potential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">Today, as businesses move more and more towards the corporate world and individual free enterprise faces unfair competition from publicly listed companies, we believe the age of individual free Multi-Level enterprise has just begun. We have high hopes in this exciting development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">However let us also warn you that there is very little free about free enterprise. It is our hope that you will pay the price with hard work, commitment and determination to build your Diamond Lifestyle (DLC) business and be an ambassador of this Company, created BY distributors FOR distributors like you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">Let us get to work and \"<strong>Aim Higher</strong>\"!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->', 'Foreword', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'foreword', '', '', '2021-03-09 00:06:06', '2021-03-08 16:06:06', '', 23, 'https://dlcph.com/read/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(22, 1, '2020-09-26 09:53:38', '2020-09-26 01:53:38', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":17,\"mediaLink\":\"https://dlcph.com/read/?attachment_id=17\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"top\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-top\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><img src=\"https://dlcph.com/read/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/founder.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-17\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"placeholder\":\"Content…\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">First of all, we would like to congratulate you in your desire to improve yourself and your lifestyle through our industry called Multi-Level Marketing (MLM) and we hope this is the vehicle that will help you discover your dreams and your full potential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Today, as businesses move more and more towards the corporate world and individual free enterprise faces unfair competition from publicly listed companies, we believe the age of individual free Multi-Level enterprise has just begun. We have high hopes in this exciting development.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>However let us also warn you that there is very little free about free enterprise. It is our hope that you will pay the price with hard work, commitment and determination to build your Diamond Lifestyle (DLC) business and be an ambassador of this Company, created BY distributors FOR distributors like you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let us get to work and \"<strong>Aim Higher</strong>\"!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->', 'Welcome to DLC Philippines', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '21-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-26 09:53:38', '2020-09-26 01:53:38', '', 21, 'https://dlcph.com/read/?p=22', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(23, 1, '2020-09-26 09:57:17', '2020-09-26 01:57:17', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/foreword/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"21\">Foreword</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First of all, we would like to congratulate you in your desire to improve yourself and your lifestyle through our industry called Multi-Level Marketing (MLM) and we hope this is the vehicle that will help you discover your dreams and your full potential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/message-from-the-founder/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"40\">Message from the Founder</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is only one solution. I wish there were another. We must write a marketing plan that also includes the 1/3 that is the profit of the owner of a MLM company into the plan. Only when we have this extra 30% can we have enough money to write a marketing plan where we can concentrate a huge portion of the bonuses to distributors who have one to three break-off legs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/aim-higher/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"42\">Aim Higher</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let us ”Aim Higher” and always strive to do more than what is expected. Do not make the mistake of doing only the minimum requirement to get your bonuses when you work your DLC business. We will be very disappointed if leaders practice this and teach their organization the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/the-spirit-of-love/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"44\">The Spirit of Love</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let the foundation spirit be the spirit of “Love”.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/commitment/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"46\">Commitment</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>INTEGRITY: We commit to provide you a company based on honesty, integrity and ethical business standards and a marketing plan that does not allow game playing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/and-god-said-no-to-a-multi-level-marketer/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"48\">And God said, “No” to a Multi-Level Marketer</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to help me love my associates<br>as much as He loves me.<br>And God said,<br>“Ah, finally you understand Multi-Level-Marketing.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/XfecVverhHw\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube 