(48, 1, '2020-09-26 10:35:33', '2020-09-26 02:35:33', '<!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaId\":15,\"mediaLink\":\"https://dlcph.com/read/?attachment_id=15\",\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"imageFill\":true,\"focalPoint\":{\"x\":\"0.50\",\"y\":\"0.55\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide is-stacked-on-mobile is-image-fill\"><figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\" style=\"background-image:url(https://dlcph.com/read/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/andgodsaidno.jpg);background-position:50% 55.00000000000001%\"><img src=\"https://dlcph.com/read/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/andgodsaidno.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-15\"/></figure><div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to give me a big organization<br>and God said, \"No.\"<br>He said He gives courage<br>and it is up to me to build it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to give me knowledge to build this organization<br>and God said, \"No.\"<br>He said He gives wisdom<br>and it is up to me to learn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to take away my pride so that I will learn<br>and God said, \"No.\"<br>He said it was not for him to take away<br>but for me to give it up.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to give me happiness<br>and God said, \"No.\"<br>He said He gives blessings<br>but happiness is up to me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to make my spirit grow<br>and God said, \"No.\"<br>He said I must grow on my own<br>but He gave me a ‘Book’ to guide me.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to help me love my associates<br>as much as He loves me.<br>And God said,<br>\"Ah, finally you understand Multi-Level-Marketing.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong><em>Eddy</em></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:media-text -->', 'And God said, \"No\" to a Multi-Level Marketer', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'and-god-said-no-to-a-multi-level-marketer', '', '', '2020-09-26 10:35:35', '2020-09-26 02:35:35', '', 23, 'https://dlcph.com/read/?page_id=48', 4, 'page', '', 0),
