(103, 1, '2020-09-26 13:42:22', '2020-09-26 05:42:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">A distributor is entitled to resign his/her distributorship by delivering to the Company a written notice within fourteen (14) days subsequent to the execution of the agreement. Any distributor withdrawing from the marketing system of the Company must wait for a one (1) year period to be qualified to apply for reparticipation into the Company, if all conditions for re-sponsoring are conformed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The distributor, who resigns from the Company, shall within thirty (30) days apply for product return pursuant to relevant rules promulgated by the Company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following products cannot be returned:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>- Products that have been opened</li><li>- Products that have been consumed</li><li>- Products that cannot be resold</li><li>- Product that DLC no longer carries</li><li>- Products that has new packaging</li><li>- Products that are within 6 months from expiry date</li><li>- Other non-DLC brand products</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The Company will buy back the products purchased within the last 180 days in the amount equal to 90% of the original product prices paid by the distributor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The Company shall give a refund to the resigning distributor when the Company receives and confirms the accuracy of the documents as mentioned above.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The application for product return shall be submitted and processed by the distributor in person to the designated area distribution center that originally supplied the products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">After completion of the above procedures, the Company will then delete from the company record the name or level of the distributor concerned. All downline distributors originally sponsored by him/her will</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Product Return by a Resigning Distributor', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'product-return-by-a-resigning-distributor', '', '', '2021-03-09 00:19:42', '2021-03-08 16:19:42', '', 72, 'https://dlcph.com/read/?page_id=103', 3, 'page', '', 0),
(104, 2, '2020-09-26 13:42:22', '2020-09-26 05:42:22', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A distributor is entitled to resign his/her distributorship by delivering to the Company a written notice within fourteen (14) days subsequent to the execution of the agreement. Any distributor withdrawing from the marketing system of the Company must wait for a one (1) year period to be qualified to apply for reparticipation into the Company, if all conditions for re-sponsoring are conformed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The distributor, who resigns from the Company, shall within thirty (30) days apply for product return pursuant to relevant rules promulgated by the Company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The following products cannot be returned:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Products that have been opened</li><li>Products that have been consumed</li><li>Products that cannot be resold</li><li>Product that DLC no longer carries</li><li>Products that has new packaging</li><li>Products that are within 6 months from expiry date</li><li>Other non-DLC brand products</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Company will buy back the products purchased within the last 180 days in the amount equal to 90% of the original product prices paid by the distributor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Company shall give a refund to the resigning distributor when the Company receives and confirms the accuracy of the documents as mentioned above.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The application for product return shall be submitted and processed by the distributor in person to the designated area distribution center that originally supplied the products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After completion of the above procedures, the Company will then delete from the company record the name or level of the distributor concerned. All downline distributors originally sponsored by him/her will</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Products Return by a Resigning Distributor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '103-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-26 13:42:22', '2020-09-26 05:42:22', '', 103, 'https://dlcph.com/read/103-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2020-09-26 13:42:58', '2020-09-26 05:42:58', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The Company will deduct all bonus(es) paid, calculated upon a specific percentage of wholesale product prices (tax excluded), directly from the amount of the return products.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">The Company will also reclaim the bonuses of upline distributors in the same line with the resigning distributor. The retrace will include the bonuses received by the distributors up to all applicable levels directly above the resigning distributor. If the product return causes any changes to other bonuses or benefits, including, but not limited to, leadership bonus, profit-sharing bonus and other incentives, the Company will reclaim the over-paid bonuses and benefits and will deduct the amount from the affected distributor(s) on the following month.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">In case the product returns affects the level or other privileges or incentives earned by a distributor, the level and benefits will also be canceled.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">Any amendments of the details and procedures, with respect to product returns, will be published from time to time.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Bonus Reclaim', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bonus-reclaim', '', '', '2021-03-09 00:20:12', '2021-03-08 16:20:12', '', 72, 'https://dlcph.com/read/?page_id=105', 4, 'page', '', 0);
