ity for buying back the saleable inventory from the departing distributor.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This \"BUY BACK\" rule will strictly be enforced.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'The “Buy Back” Rule in cases of Game Playing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '107-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-09-26 13:43:31', '2020-09-26 05:43:31', '', 107, 'https://dlcph.com/read/107-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
