(277, 2, '2020-10-16 19:32:49', '2020-10-16 11:32:49', '<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/foreword/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"21\">Foreword</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>First of all, we would like to congratulate you in your desire to improve yourself and your lifestyle through our industry called Multi-Level Marketing (MLM) and we hope this is the vehicle that will help you discover your dreams and your full potential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/message-from-the-founder/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"40\">Message from the Founder</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There is only one solution. I wish there were another. We must write a marketing plan that also includes the 1/3 that is the profit of the owner of a MLM company into the plan. Only when we have this extra 30% can we have enough money to write a marketing plan where we can concentrate a huge portion of the bonuses to distributors who have one to three break-off legs.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/aim-higher/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"42\">Aim Higher</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let us ”Aim Higher” and always strive to do more than what is expected. Do not make the mistake of doing only the minimum requirement to get your bonuses when you work your DLC business. We will be very disappointed if leaders practice this and teach their organization the same.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/the-spirit-of-love/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"44\">The Spirit of Love</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Let the foundation spirit be the spirit of “Love”.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/commitment/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"46\">Commitment</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>INTEGRITY: We commit to provide you a company based on honesty, integrity and ethical business standards and a marketing plan that does not allow game playing.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/i-am-dlc/and-god-said-no-to-a-multi-level-marketer/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"48\">And God said, “No” to a Multi-Level Marketer</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I asked God to help me love my associates<br>as much as He loves me.<br>And God said,<br>“Ah, finally you understand Multi-Level-Marketing.”</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/XfecVverhHw\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/XfecVverhHw\n</div></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->', 'I. Am. DLC.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-16 19:32:49', '2020-10-16 11:32:49', '', 23, 'https://dlcph.com/read/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(278, 2, '2020-10-16 19:33:43', '2020-10-16 11:33:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<p class=\"has-large-font-size\">Be Your Own Boss</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/b-y-o-b/getting-started/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"55\">Getting Started</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>An individual who is at least eighteen (18) years or older (may vary depending on the laws of every country) can join DLC. However, DLC reserves the right not to accept an application or reject/return an application after acceptance.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/b-y-o-b/responsoring/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"57\">Distributor’s Responsoring</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Any active distributor can responsor other distributors after six (6) months of inactivity. Distributors who requested termination or are terminated can also be responsored after they have been inactive for six (6) months subject to the approval of the Company.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/b-y-o-b/ordering/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"59\">Rules of Product Ordering</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All registered distributors are authorized to purchase directly from the Company.<br>Products shall be paid for in cash or other modes set by DLC. All transactions shall be completed and consummated at the point of sale upon release of invoice.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4><a href=\"https://dlcph.com/read/b-y-o-b/delivery-system/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"61\">Delivery System</a></h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Place your order, pay for your order, get confirmation</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:separator {\"className\":\"is-style-wide\"} -->\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator is-style-wide\"/>\n<!-- /wp:separator -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer -->\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>Turn Your Expenses to Income</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/LfqL1wiD29E\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/LfqL1wiD29E\n</div><figcaption>Turn Your Expenses to Income (Tagalog)</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:core-embed/youtube {\"url\":\"https://youtu.be/AkiZC82Qcdw\",\"type\":\"video\",\"providerNameSlug\":\"youtube\",\"className\":\"wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\nhttps://youtu.be/AkiZC82Qcdw\n</div><figcaption>Turn Your Expenses to Income (Bisaya)</figcaption></figure>\n<!-- /wp:core-embed/youtube -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'B. Y. O. B.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '25-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-16 19:33:43', '2020-10-16 11:33:43', '', 25, 'https://dlcph.com/read/25-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
