.</li></ul></li><li>0%, 6%, 15%, 21%, 24% distributors will not be able to receive any Override Bonus on any distributor who is at the same level in their sponsored group. However, they will qualify to receive PV from such sources for move-up purposes.</li><li>There is a no reversion clause at the 6% level but there is a cycle reversion to 6% at the 15%, 21% and 24% levels.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Semi-Monthly Bonus', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '118-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 22:55:34', '2021-03-08 14:55:34', '', 118, 'https://dlcph.com/read/118-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
