 qualifying period).<br></li><li><strong>Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphire pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>A blue gemstone is to remind you to be grateful and loyal. While most companies have no right to demand loyalty from their leaders, we believe DLC has every right to demand loyalty from you. DLC also expect you to teach this spirit and culture in our Company.</em><br></li><li><strong>Super Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphires pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br></li><li><strong>Level 12 Profit Sharing Diamond Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 12 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 12 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Diamond pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br