th Emeralds pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br></li><li><strong>Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphire pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>A blue gemstone is to remind you to be grateful and loyal. While most companies have no right to demand loyalty from their leaders, we believe DLC has every right to demand loyalty from you. DLC also expect you to teach this spirit and culture in our Company.</em><br></li><li><strong>Super Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphires pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br></li><li><strong>Level 12 Profit Sharing Diamond Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 12 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 12 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Diamond pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>A diamond is the gem of all gems. It is also a name we used for our Company. Congratulations! You have reached the top. Be as flawless as you can, as you are DLC. Continue to do your part in your Company and help your leaders to also become Diamonds. Find and build your acres of Diamonds, and enjoy your Diamond Lifestyle.</em><br><br>At this point, we would like to remind you not to lose your head to success. Accept the recognition, applause, respect and love from your downlines and crosslines for the achievements and hard work you have done but do not forget: this was made possible by DLC. To whom more is given, more is expected. We will be stricter with you than we do with other leaders.<br></li><li><strong>Super Level 12 Profit Sharing Diamond Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 12 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 12 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Diamonds pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager Bonuses and Pins', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 23:23:38', '2021-03-08 15:23:38', '', 294, 'https://dlcph.com/read/294-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
