(408, 2, '2021-03-08 23:48:33', '2021-03-08 15:48:33', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Quarterly Profit Sharing Bonus Pay Out Program</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"jt\"} -->\n<p class=\"jt\">DLC will pay out 8% of the company’s quarterly sales at POV as Quarterly Profit Sharing Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Twelve Million (12,000,000) Quarterly POV. Qualification requirement: All Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers must qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus at least five (5) cycles in the three (3) months period, need not be consecutive.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><strong>What is the qualifying period for the Quarterly Profit Sharing?</strong><br><p class=\"jt\">Qualifying for our Quarterly Profit Sharing Bonus is from<br>Cycle 1 to Cycle 6 (January to March),<br>Cycle 7 to Cycle 12 (April to June),<br>Cycle 13 to Cycle 18 (July to September),<br>Cycle 19 to Cycle 24 (October to December).</p></li><li><strong>Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager (8%)</strong><br>Super 4000 QPSM = 24% x 5 cycles = 3%<br>Level 2 QPSM = 2 Managers at 24% x 5 cycles = 2%<br>Level 3 QPSM = 3 Managers at 24% x 5 cycles = 2%<br>Level 4 QPSM = 4 Managers at 24% x 5 cycles = 1%<br><br></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super 4000 QPSM 3%.</strong> Any 24% and above distributor who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products and qualifies for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus at least five (5) cycles in the Quarterly Profit Sharing period using proper MLM principles is considered a Super 4000 QPSM. The 3% of the Quarterly POV will be divided equally among those who qualify.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 2 QPSM 2%.</strong> The share a leader will receive is dependent on his/her Profit Sharing Points (PSP) plus 30% of the PSP of his/her 1st Generation Active Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers qualified for the program. The PSP is the sum of the Personal Point Value (PPV: Personal Sales PV) and the Group Point Value (GPV: Group Sales PV of all personally sponsored Distributors below 24%) of the PSM for the Profit Sharing Period. The 2% of the Quarterly POV will be divided equally among those who qualify.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 3 QPSM 2%.</strong> The share a leader will receive is dependent on his/her Profit Sharing Points (PSP) plus 30% of the PSP of all of his/her 1st Generation Active Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers qualified for the program plus 10% of the PSP of all active second generation Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers and below (infinity). The 2% of the Quarterly POV will be divided equally among those who qualify.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 3 QPSM 2%.</strong> The share a leader will receive is dependent on his/her Profit Sharing Points (PSP) plus 30% of the PSP of all of his/her 1st Generation Active Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers qualified for the program plus 10% of the PSP of all active second generation Quarterly Profit Sharing Managers and below (infinity). The 2% of the Quarterly POV will be divided equally among those who qualify.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">The Quarterly Profit Sharing Program is a benefit designed for leaders who can build a strong, healthy and stable network. Retailing and sponsoring of new distributors are the keys to enjoy the Quarterly Profit Sharing Bonuses. DLC reserves the right to make adjustments.</p></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br><strong>Quarterly Profit Sharing Pin Recognition</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">In recognition of the achievements and impressive leadership qualities of distributors, the Company will award DLC pins to eligible Managers and Profit Sharing Managers. These pins should be worn proudly to symbolize the hard work and leadership qualities of these distributors.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">A Pin Manager can proudly wear the pin he/she had been awarded even if his/her organization no longer qualifies for the sales requirement for that pin.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">In order to qualify for Recognized Manager, Profit Sharing Manager, Pearl Profit Sharing Manager, Ruby Profit Sharing Manager, Emerald Profit Sharing Manager, Sapphire Profit Sharing Manager and Diamond Profit Sharing Manager Pins, he/she should comply with the guidelines as explained in our Company Policy.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Whoever qualifies for the profit sharing pin must take the initiative to confirm the eligible line/s by submitting a Profit Sharing Pin Confirmation Form within fifteen (15) days after the cut-off of the qualifying period to be awarded the pins during the rally.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Business Builder Manager Pin.</strong> Any 24% and above distributor who qualifies for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus at least five (5) cycles in the Quarterly Profit Sharing period using proper MLM principles is considered a Business Builder (BB) Manager. A first time Business Builder must submit a Confirmation Form to the Company and upon confirmation, he/she will be awarded a Gold pin during the Quarterly Profit Sharing Rally.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 1 Profit Sharing Manager Pin</strong>. Any manager who qualifies for the Level 1 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 1 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 1 Profit Sharing Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 1 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 1 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 2 Profit Sharing Pearl Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 2 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 2 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Pearl pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 2 Profit Sharing Pearl Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 2 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 2 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Pearls pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 3 Profit Sharing Ruby Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 3 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 3 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Ruby pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>The ruby is a red-hot gemstone, we encourage you to remain red-hot and help DLC motivate other people, as managers at this level are the most excited.</em></p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 3 Profit Sharing Ruby Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 3 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 3 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Rubies pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 6 Profit Sharing Emerald Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 6 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 6 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Emerald pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period). <br><br><em>Why a green gem stone at this level? This is to remind you to be humble and have a good learning attitude. Do not think you now know everything and stop learning. Keep on improving yourself to be a better person. Proud people are people who feel insecure.</em></p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 6 Profit Sharing Emerald Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 6 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 6 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Emeralds pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphire pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>A blue gemstone is to remind you to be grateful and loyal. While most companies have no right to demand loyalty from their leaders, we believe DLC has every right to demand loyalty from you. DLC also expect you to teach this spirit and culture in our Company.</em></p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 9 Profit Sharing Sapphire Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 9 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 9 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Sapphires pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Level 12 Profit Sharing Diamond Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Level 12 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for two (2) consecutive Quarterly Profit Sharing Periods must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 12 Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Gold Profit Sharing Manager with Diamond pin at the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).<br><br><em>A diamond is the gem of all gems. It is also a name we used for our Company. Congratulations! You have reached the top. Be as flawless as you can, as you are DLC. Continue to do your part in your Company and help your leaders to also become Diamonds. Find and build your acres of Diamonds, and enjoy your Diamond Lifestyle.</em><br><br>At this point, we would like to remind you not to lose your head to success. Accept the recognition, applause, respect and love from your downlines and crosslines for the achievements and hard work you have done but do not forget: this was made possible by DLC. To whom more is given, more is expected. We will be stricter with you than we do with other leaders.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\"><strong>Super Level 12 Profit Sharing Diamond Manager Pin.</strong> Any manager who qualifies for the Super Level 12 Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager for four (4) consecutive Profit Sharing Periods within the calendar year must submit a Quarterly Profit Sharing Confirmation Form and, after the validation of the company, will become a Recognized Level 12 Super Profit Sharing Manager and awarded a Platinum Profit Sharing Manager with Diamonds pin during the Recognition Rally. (Note that the qualifying managers must be the same persons for the duration of the qualifying period).</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Quarterly Profit Sharing Manager Bonuses and Pins', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 23:48:33', '2021-03-08 15:48:33', '', 294, 'https://dlcph.com/read/294-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(410, 2, '2021-03-08 23:49:41', '2021-03-08 15:49:41', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All Gold Managers can qualify for our Semi-Monthly profit sharing program defined as follows:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">The Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 10% of the total national sales volume paid at POV equally divided by the total number of qualifiers for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Qualifiers for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be guaranteed with an income of at least Ten Thousand Pesos (Php 10,000.00) in the qualifying cycle.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Distributors who accumulate at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle in the local country can qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus provided that the International Distributor had 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the qualifying cycle in the local country upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV.<br><br><strong>DLC is very proud to be the first to conceptualize the Ultimate Infinity Plan in the World of MLM with our Profit Sharing System based on National Sales at only minimal sales volume.</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded\nproducts and breaks off one (1) or more lines that qualifies for our Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 6% of the total national sales volume paid at POV equally divided by the total number of qualifiers for the Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Gold SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local line\'s qualifying cycle and break off one (1) or more local lines that qualifies for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, also qualify for Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the\nrequirements stated in 3.3.1.4.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 500 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off two (2) or more lines that qualifies for our Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 2 Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV equally divided by the total number of qualifiers for the Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off two (2) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus in full, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4.<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify for Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus and above in the local country and accumulate at least 2000 PV but less than 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle in the local country can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV, provided that the International Manager had qualified in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying week.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Points (SMPSP). SMPSP is computed at the sum of the following:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>8 points for every first generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.\n</li><li>4 points for every second generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.\n</li><li>2 points for every third generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.\n</li><li>1 point for every fourth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.\n</li><li>1 point for every fifth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager qualified for the program.\n</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off three (3) or more lines that qualifies for our\nSemi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 3 Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.<br><br></li><li>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off three (3) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 3 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off four (4) or more lines that qualifies for our\nSemi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 1.5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but\nnot 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the week of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off four (4) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 4 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '152-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 23:49:41', '2021-03-08 15:49:41', '', 152, 'https://dlcph.com/read/152-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(412, 2, '2021-03-08 23:50:31', '2021-03-08 15:50:31', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All Gold Managers can qualify for our Semi-Monthly profit sharing program defined as follows:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">The Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 10% of the total national sales volume paid at POV equally divided by the total number of qualifiers for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Qualifiers for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be guaranteed with an income of at least Ten Thousand Pesos (Php 10,000.00) in the qualifying cycle.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Distributors who accumulate at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle in the local country can qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus provided that the International Distributor had 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the qualifying cycle in the local country upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV.<br><br><strong>DLC is very proud to be the first to conceptualize the Ultimate Infinity Plan in the World of MLM with our Profit Sharing System based on National Sales at only minimal sales volume.</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager 