 in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying week.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Points (SMPSP). SMPSP is computed at the sum of the following:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>8 points for every first generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>4 points for every second generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>2 points for every third generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>1 point for every fourth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>1 point for every fifth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager qualified for the program.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off three (3) or more lines that qualifies for our\nSemi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 3 Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off three (3) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 3 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>A distributor qualifies for the Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off four (4) or more lines that qualifies for our\nSemi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 1.5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but\nnot 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the week of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.<br><br></li><li>International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off four (4) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 4 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '152-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 23:52:36', '2021-03-08 15:52:36', '', 152, 'https://dlcph.com/read/152-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(419, 2, '2021-03-08 23:53:15', '2021-03-08 15:53:15', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All Gold Managers can qualify for our Semi-Monthly profit sharing program defined as follows:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">The Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 10% of the total national sales volume paid at POV equally divided by the total number of qualifiers for the Gold Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Qualifiers for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be guaranteed with an income of at least Ten Thousand Pesos (Php 10,000.00) in the qualifying cycle.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Distributors who accumulate at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle in the local country can qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus provided that the International Distributor had 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the qualifying cycle in the local country upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV.<br><br><strong>DLC is very proud to be the first to conceptualize the Ultimate Infinity Plan in the World of MLM with our Profit Sharing System based on National Sales at only minimal sales volume.</strong></li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit 