onus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off two (2) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus in full, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Managers who qualify for Level 2 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus and above in the local country and accumulate at least 2000 PV but less than 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle in the local country can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV, provided that the International Manager had qualified in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying week.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Points (SMPSP). SMPSP is computed at the sum of the following:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>8 points for every first generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>4 points for every second generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>2 points for every third generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>1 point for every fourth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing\nManager qualified for the program.</li><li>1 point for every fifth generation Active Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager qualified for the program.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off three (3) or more lines that qualifies for our\nSemi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 3 Weekly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 3 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off three (3) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 3 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li><p class=\"jt\">A distributor qualifies for the Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus when a distributor does at least 40 PV as personal sales from DLC-branded products and breaks off four (4) or more lines that qualifies for our Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus will be 1.5% of the total national sales volume paid at POV divided by the total SMPSP of all qualifiers for Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus multiplied by the SMPSP of the distributor.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager also qualifies for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager who does at least 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the cycle of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, also qualifies for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">Level 4 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Managers who does at least 2000 PV but not 4000 PV from non-manager group total sales volume for the week of which 40 PV is personal sales from DLC-branded products, can qualify for fifty percent (50%) of the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus.</p></li><li><p class=\"jt\">International Managers who qualify in the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus in their Home Base two (2) cycles before the local lines\' qualifying cycle and break off four (4) or more lines that qualify for the Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus, at least one of which is a local line, also qualify for Level 4 SemiMonthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus upon reaching the National Sales Target (NST) of Two Million (2,000,000) Semi-Monthly POV. They also qualify for Level 3, Level 2 and Level 1 Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus. To qualify for the Gold Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Manager Bonus, the International Manager must qualify the requirements stated in 3.3.1.4 or 3.3.3.7.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->', 'Semi-Monthly Profit Sharing Bonus', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '152-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-03-08 23:53:15', '2021-03-08 15:53:15', '', 152, 'https://dlcph.com/read/152-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
